      "title": "One-hour power cuts scheduled for next four days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) says it has approved power cuts of 01 hour daily from September 06th to 09th.",
        "Accordingly, the power cuts for the next four days are to be imposed as follows:",
